#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/solutions.adoc:6
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/solutions.adoc:6
msgid "This appendix contains the answers and additional information to all of the review quizzes."
msgstr "Este apéndice contiene las respuestas e información adicional a todos los cuestionarios de repaso."

